com.digitalpersona.uareu

Interface Fid.Fiv

  • Enclosing interface:
    Fid

    public static interface Fid.Fiv
    Class represents Fingerprint Image View (FIV).

    Class reflect ANSI INSITS 381-2004 and ISO IEC 19794-4-2005 formats.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      byte[] getData()
      Returns complete binary data of a view, including view header
      int getFingerPosition()
      Returns finger position, from Tables 5 and 6 in "ANSI INSITS 381-2004"
      int getHeight()
      Returns width of the fingerprint view, in pixels
      byte[] getImageData()
      Returns view image data
      int getImpressionType()
      Returns impression type, from Table 7 in "ANSI INSITS 381-2004"
      int getQuality()
      Returns quality, 1 - 100 for ISO; 1 - 100, 254 for ANSI
      int getViewCnt()
      Returns number of views associated with this finger, must be greater or equal to 1
      int getViewNumber()
      Returns view number, from 1 to 256
      int getWidth()
      Returns height of the fingerprint view, in pixels
